trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of menu items in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling for menyelementer med en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The MenuItemCollection class is used to store and manage a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem> objects in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen MenuItemCollection brukes til å lagre og behandle en samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem>objekter i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control uses the MenuItemCollection class to store its root menu items in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.Items%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontrollen bruker klassen MenuItemCollection til å lagre de primære menyelementene med den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.Items%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.Items%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.source: This collection is also used for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem.ChildItems%2A> property of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem> object to store a menu item's submenu items (if any).
trans-unit.target: Denne samlingen brukes også for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem.ChildItems%2A>for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem>objektet til å lagre undermenyelementer for et menyelement (Hvis noen).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem.ChildItems%2A>

trans-unit.source: The MenuItemCollection class supports several ways to access the items in the collection: - Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.Item%2A> indexer to directly retrieve a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem> object at a specific zero-based index.
trans-unit.target: Klassen MenuItemCollection støtter flere metoder for å få tilgang til elementer i samlingen:-Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.Item%2A>indekserer til å hente direkte en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem>objektet i en bestemt nullbaserte indeksen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.Item%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.GetEnumerator%2A> method to create an enumerator that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: -Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.GetEnumerator%2A>metode for å opprette en opplisting som kan brukes til å gå gjennom samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.GetEnumerator%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.CopyTo%2A> method to copy the contents of the collection into an array.
trans-unit.target: -Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.CopyTo%2A>metode for å kopiere innholdet i samlingen til en matrise.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.CopyTo%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can programmatically manage a MenuItemCollection object by adding and removing <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem> objects.
trans-unit.target: Du kan programmatisk administrere en MenuItemCollection-objektet ved å legge til og fjerne <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem>objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem>

trans-unit.source: To add menu items to the collection, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.Add%2A> or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.AddAt%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil legge til menyelementer i samlingen, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.Add%2A>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.AddAt%2A>metode.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.AddAt%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: To remove nodes from the collection, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.Remove%2A>, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A>, or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.Clear%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil fjerne noder fra samlingen, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.Remove%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A>, eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.Clear%2A>metode.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.Clear%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.Remove%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > When the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control is bound to a data source, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.Items%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem.ChildItems%2A> collections are automatically populated each time binding occurs.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Når den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontrollen er bundet til en datakilde i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.Items%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem.ChildItems%2A>samlinger fylles ut automatisk hver gang bindingen forekommer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem.ChildItems%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.Items%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.source: Any changes to the collections between bindings will be lost.
trans-unit.target: Endringer i samlinger mellom bindinger vil gå tapt.

trans-unit.source: To retain these changes, either update the data source or manually rebuild the collection each time you bind.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil beholde disse endringene, oppdatere datakilden eller Bygg samlingen hver gang du binde manuelt.

trans-unit.source: The MenuItemCollection class contains properties and methods that allow you to retrieve information about the collection itself.
trans-unit.target: Klassen MenuItemCollection inneholder egenskaper og metoder som gjør det mulig å hente informasjon om samlingen seg selv.

trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil finne ut hvor mange elementer som i samlingen, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.Count%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Count property is also commonly used to determine whether a collection is empty.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen antall brukes også vanligvis til å finne ut om en samling er tom.

trans-unit.source: Gets an object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter et objekt som kan brukes til å synkronisere tilgang til den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The SyncRoot property provides a synchronized version of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection> object that can be used with synchronizing (threading) code.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen SyncRoot gir en synkroniserte versjon av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection>objekt som kan brukes med synkronisering (trådmodell) code.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.IsSynchronized%2A> property of this class always returns `false`, which indicates that the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection> class is not synchronized (not thread safe).
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION] > I <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.IsSynchronized%2A>for dette klasse alltid returnerer `false`, som angir at det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection>klasse er ikke synkronisert (ikke tråden trygt).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection.IsSynchronized%2A>

trans-unit.source: Synchronizing code must perform operations on the SyncRoot object of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection> collection, not directly on the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection> object itself.
trans-unit.target: Synkroniserer kode må utføre operasjoner på SyncRoot-objekt av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection>samling, ikke direkte på den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection>selve objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: This ensures proper operation of collections that are derived from other objects.
trans-unit.target: Dette sikrer ordentlig med samlinger som er avledet fra andre objekter.

trans-unit.source: Specifically, it maintains proper synchronization with other threads that might be simultaneously modifying the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: Nærmere bestemt den opprettholder riktig synkronisering med andre tråder som kan være samtidig endring av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The object returned in this implementation is the <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> object used to store the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem> objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Objektet returnerte i denne implementeringen av <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList>objektet brukes til å lagre den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem>objekter i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem> </xref:System.Collections.ArrayList>

trans-unit.source: Enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: Lister opp i en samling vil si gjelder ikke sikker.

trans-unit.source: Even when a collection is synchronized, other threads could still modify the collection, causing the enumerator to throw an exception.
trans-unit.target: Selv når en samling synkroniseres, kan andre tråder fortsatt endre samlingen, fører til at enumeratoren til Iverksett et unntak.

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can either lock the collection during the entire enumeration or catch the exceptions resulting from changes made by other threads.
trans-unit.target: For å garantere tråd sikkerhetsnivået under opplisting, kan du låse samlingen under hele opplistingen eller opp unntak som er et resultat av endringer foretatt av andre tråder.

trans-unit.source: For more information on the SyncRoot property, see the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A> property of the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> interface.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om egenskapen SyncRoot, se den <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A>-egenskapen til det <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection> </xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A>
